{"tid":245030,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利迷不滿托利斯慶祝車路士奪冠","createTime":"2017-05-16T01:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T16:56:11.000Z","uid":6555,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"788c40528cde1c456cbd4b4d80c82ecc87ebbb90","tid":245030,"uid":6555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T01:49:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Liverpool fans are angry with Fernando Torres for his reaction to Chelsea winning the Premier League title</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nChelsea won the Premier League title after beating West Brom on Friday.<br />\n<br />\nAnd as to be expected a flood of current players, former players, wannabe players, celebrity fans, and everyone else for that matter took to various social media sites to congratulate Antonio Conte's side on the achievement.<br />\n<br />\nHowever, one former Chelsea player represented another big team in the Premier League once up a time, and his show of public support for the Blues made Reds fans, well, blue.<br />\n<br />\nFernando Torres signed for Liverpool back in 2007 and became one of the greatest centre forwards the club had ever seen.<br />\n<br />\nIn 2011 he made a move to London to join Chelsea in a deal worth a staggering &pound;50million, breaking many a heart on Merseyside in the process.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pics.onsizzle.com/o-a-torres-torres-fernando-congrats-champions-now-lets-fight-20864497.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics.onsizzle.com%2Fo-a-torres-torres-fernando-congrats-champions-now-lets-fight-20864497.png&h=25687620&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTaking to Twitter he wrote: &quot;Congrats Champions!!! Now let's fight for the FA Cup.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nAnd well, the message went down like a lead balloon among the Liverpool fans.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/news/liverpool-fans-angry-fernando-torres-10415723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Fnews%2Fliverpool-fans-angry-fernando-torres-10415723&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=f3a6c8d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/news/liverpool-fans-angry-fernando-torres-10415723</a>"},{"pid":"808fff21ef29b83ca9680c798b5b624c9165b1e0","tid":245030,"uid":76412,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T01:56:27.000Z","msg":"屌，我見兩者無衝突咪慶祝下囉，唔講以為利記屈居亞軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3efbac9dacd1e97a9e0599c27d59968821d5c073","tid":245030,"uid":19196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T01:58:50.000Z","msg":"關猁撚事"},{"pid":"01c8ec328b79f90b9acf22806b0d2c80d2e52e93","tid":245030,"uid":60794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T02:00:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌，我見兩者無衝突咪慶祝下囉，唔講以為利記屈居亞軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年都係車仔逞強利記先屈居亞軍姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59e013f4b1deacc7b230d648c4b780a8f545f78","tid":245030,"uid":3194,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T02:01:28.000Z","msg":"你猁拎到佢咪慶祝囉垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efd2478011e79399233f589d6afb718527c04dd","tid":245030,"uid":23190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T02:02:51.000Z","msg":"王子仲欠你班猁d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1c4fb02ed764a1ad357de44dde85546911ca4c","tid":245030,"uid":760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T02:03:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>王子仲欠你班猁d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n欠一個英超冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729629c01fb5220e429239364d9e8bd2ede8d05e","tid":245030,"uid":56947,"like":0,"disl